啲目標再分區<br />\n香港人 升級行動啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:58:09.000Z","msg":"分散五區只會得返勇武自己玩<br />\n要儲大氣入港島賀佢老母<br />\n<br />\n利申：理性討論呀，你分五區我都唔割"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:01:02.000Z","msg":"主要係港島啲狗一定重兵<br />\n分區姐係分散原本為數唔多嘅勇武手足<br />\n更加冇可以攻到港島<br />\n所以要攻港島就一定要集中火力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞掂哂先好走"},{"pid":"50374474c54338ed8838881cf6e5ebf2e87b6281","tid":1600793,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:01:17.000Z","msg":"[緊急呼籲］行動post 全部人幫我推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1600296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1600296</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3a26d422a2727f2114185b31db0cd759829483f3","tid":1600793,"uid":125542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:02:34.000Z","msg":"係囖係囖 入港島俾狗狗拉曬 送個大禮俾中共"},{"pid":"f15dee3a6a8096972c24803eb76aa1c80728de3e","tid":1600793,"uid":76867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:03:51.000Z","msg":"夠 膽 就 拉 撚 哂 港 島 所 有 人<br />\n十一你咪照出tg水炮車<br />\n我睇你國慶仲有咩面子可言<br />\nParty我就開硬既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b62b3a2c96bfa4fb44eae03b01019528cc98190","tid":1600793,"uid":17244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a26d422a2727f2114185b31db0cd759829483f3","tid":1600793,"uid":125542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:02:34.000Z","msg":"係囖係囖 入港島俾狗狗拉曬 送個大禮俾中共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:07:07.000Z","msg":"咁十一唔一定要由朝打到晚架嘛<br />\n和勇合一"},{"pid":"2b9e767e9c9e8d8422cdf6f9751c461e701c0c3e","tid":1600793,"uid":17244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f15dee3a6a8096972c24803eb76aa1c80728de3e","tid":1600793,"uid":76867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:03:51.000Z","msg":"夠 膽 就 拉 撚 哂 港 島 所 有 人<br />\n十一你咪照出tg水炮車<br />\n我睇你國慶仲有咩面子可言<br />\nParty我就開硬既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"re